.TH "BOSCO\-STOP" "3" "July 2019" "" ""
.SH "NAME"
\fBbosco-stop\fR \- Stop all of the running Node and Docker processes\.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.P
.RS 2
.nf
bosco stop
bosco stop \-r <repoPattern>
.fi
.RE
.SH DESCRIPTION
.P
This command stops all of the Node and Docker processes launched via the \fBbosco run\fP command\.
.SH COMMAND LINE OPTIONS
.SS \-r, \-\-repo
.RS 0
.IP \(bu 2
Default: \.*
.IP \(bu 2
Type: String

.RE
.P
This sets a regex string to use to filter the repostory list\.
